"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     50 mg (10): $122.65",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F5183726\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Pelvic exam prior to each course of therapy; basal body temperature, serum progesterone, urinary luteinizing hormone; follicular growth and endometrial thickness may be useful in some cases; pregnancy test prior to repeat courses",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block rer drugH1Div\" id=\"F153201\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Reference Range",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Serum progesterone: Ovulation generally occurs with levels &ge;3 ng/mL; best results with levels &gt;10 ng/mL",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
